net.sf.beezle.mork.scanner

Class FA

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.beezle.mork.scanner.FA

  • public class FA
extends Object
    Finite automaton, deteministic or non-deterministic. Has at least 1 state. Always has a start state. Maintains a set of end states.
